title: Rabbis Join Yerushalayim Protest
body: Hundreds of thousands expected in Yerushalayim for a mass Atzeres Tefillah protest against the government's giyus decree and yeshiva bochurim arrests. Gedolei Yisroel will join the masses on balconies along Yirmiyahu and Sarei Yisrael Streets for tefillah.
